The paper discusses the application of deep learning techniques to analyze electronic health records (EHRs), which involves natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CY (Computers and Society) as the paper discusses the impact of EHRs on healthcare. The paper also involves NLP, which suggests cs.CL (Computation and Language) as another possible category. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of deep learning for prediction tasks, which suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as another possible category. Finally, the paper involves data management and analysis, which suggests cs.DB (Databases) as a possible category.
